      • getCurrentValue

        public java.math.BigInteger getCurrentValue()
        Get the current sequence value. if nextMin=1,nextMax=3,then 1,2,3 will be returned. if (nextMin == nextMax), then only 1 sequence will be returned.
        返回:
        a sequence, or null if current value has reached the end of sequence range.
